OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'sweeping reform'
OL,4,Cin official response to Grenfell
OL,5,CInquiry
OL,7,FThe Government has pledged "tough
OL,8,Faction" on the construction industry
OL,9,Fand stronger rights for residents as
OL,10,Fit formally accepted recommendations
OL,11,Fmade by the Grenfell Tower Inquiry
OL,12,Ffinal report.
OL,14,FA group representing some of the
OL,15,Fbereaved welcomed the commitments but
OL,16,Fwarned it will be paying "close
OL,17,Fattention" to how they progress.
