OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'sweeping reform'
OL,4,Cin official response to Grenfell
OL,5,CInquiry
OL,7,FThe Government said it is accepting in
OL,8,Ffull 49 of the 58 recommendations made
OL,9,Fby Sir Martin Moore-Bick when he
OL,10,Fpublished his long-awaited report in
OL,11,FSeptember.
OL,13,FThe report concluded the fatal 2017
OL,14,Ffire in west London had been the
OL,15,F"culmination of decades of failure"
OL,16,Facross government and the building
OL,17,Findustry.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@cO]
