OL,5,CInquiry
OL,7,FThe Government said the remaining nine
OL,8,Frecommendations are being accepted "in
OL,9,Fprinciple", with some requiring
OL,10,F"further consideration" through
OL,11,Fconsultations.
OL,13,FThis includes a key recommendation for
OL,14,Fa single regulator for the
OL,15,Fconstruction industry, which the
OL,16,Freport said had become "too complex
OL,17,Fand fragmented".
OL,26,@pD@dOUqD@JO]rD@AOUrD@WO]xD@XOUyD@OO]
