OL,7,FOn Wednesday, the Government said
OL,8,Fwhile it is committed to establishing
OL,9,Fa single regulator, it does not
OL,10,Fbelieve it would be "appropriate" for
OL,11,Fthat organisation to undertake testing
OL,12,Fand certification of construction
OL,13,Fproducts, or issue certificates of
OL,14,Fcompliance.
OL,26,@rD@UOUrD@aO]
