OL,5,CInquiry
OL,7,FArguing this would "create a new
OL,8,Fconflict of interest within the
OL,9,Fregulator", the Government said it
OL,10,Fwill instead work to strengthen
OL,11,Foversight of existing bodies through
OL,12,Freforms to the construction products
OL,13,Fregime.
OL,15,FIt has launched a consultation,
OL,16,Frunning until May, on regulatory
OL,17,Freform in the sector to "improve
OL,18,Fpublic safety, rebuild public trust
OL,19,Fand ensure the Grenfell Tower tragedy
OL,20,Fcannot be repeated".
OL,26,@oD@TOUqD@JO]yD@YOU|D@SO]
