OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'sweeping reform'
OL,4,Cin official response to Grenfell
OL,5,CInquiry
OL,7,FThe timeline for wider change is set
OL,8,Fout in phases, with a suggestion some
OL,9,Freforms are unlikely to be delivered
OL,10,Fbefore 2028 ` 11 years on from the
OL,11,Ffire which claimed the lives of 72
OL,12,Fpeople.
OL,14,FIn its update, the Government said it
OL,15,Fis "committed to delivering meaningful
OL,16,Fchange as quickly as possible" but
OL,17,Fthat "given the scale of further
OL,18,Fchange needed, including legislative,
OL,19,Fwe intend to deliver these further
OL,20,Freforms using a three-phased approach
OL,21,Fover the course of this Parliament".
OL,26,@wD@DOUxD@^O]yD@FOU}D@cO]
