OL,7,FSeven organisations criticised in last
OL,8,Fyear's report are also being
OL,9,Finvestigated for possible bans on
OL,10,Fpublic contracts, using powers under
OL,11,Fthe Procurement Act 2023.
OL,13,FThe Cabinet Office is launching
OL,14,Finvestigations to establish whether
OL,15,Fprofessional misconduct has taken
OL,16,Fplace and vowed decisions on debarment
OL,17,Fwill be made "at pace".
