OL,7,FIn a lengthy document detailing its
OL,8,Fwider response, the Government also
OL,9,Fsaid it is "committed to exploring
OL,10,Ffurther reforms to deliver systemic
OL,11,Fchange to how residents' voices are
OL,12,Fheard and reliably acted upon".
OL,14,FThe inquiry report noted how the
OL,15,Frelationship between Grenfell Tower
OL,16,Flandlords and residents in the years
OL,17,Fbefore the fire was "increasingly
OL,18,Fcharacterised by distrust, dislike,
OL,19,Fpersonal antagonism and anger".
OL,26,@qD@LOUtD@^O]yD@UOU{D@^O]
