OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'sweeping reform'
OL,4,Cin official response to Grenfell
OL,5,CInquiry
OL,7,FDeputy Prime Minister Angela Rayner,
OL,8,Fwho is also Housing Secretary, said:
OL,9,F"We are acting on all of the inquiry's
OL,10,Ffindings, and today set out our full
OL,11,Fresponse, detailing the tough action
OL,12,Fwe are taking to drive change and
OL,13,Freform the system to ensure no
OL,14,Fcommunity will ever have to face a
OL,15,Ftragedy like Grenfell ever again.
OL,17,F"That means greater accountability,
OL,18,Fstronger regulation, and putting
OL,19,Fresidents at the heart of decision-
OL,20,Fmaking.
OL,26,@qD@AO]yD@AOU
