OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'sweeping reform'
OL,4,Cin official response to Grenfell
OL,5,CInquiry
OL,7,F"We must deliver the fundamental
OL,8,Fchange required. We owe that to the
OL,9,FGrenfell community, to the country,
OL,10,Fand to the memory of those who lost
OL,11,Ftheir lives."
OL,13,FGrenfell Next of Kin, a group
OL,14,Frepresenting some of the bereaved,
OL,15,Fsaid it will be "paying close
OL,16,Fattention to these words and
OL,17,Fintentions" from Government, as it
OL,18,Frepeated criticism of the "grave
OL,19,Fmistakes, failures, corruption" it
OL,20,Fsaid had led to the deaths.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@MO]wD@QOUyD@KO]zD@[OU{D@_O]
