OL,5,CInquiry
OL,7,FThe group: "We can never forget our
OL,8,Fbeloved kin and we can never forgive
OL,9,Fthe negligence and corruption that led
OL,10,Fto their deaths.
OL,12,F"The injustice is so great and the
OL,13,Fmeasures being put in place now with
OL,14,Fnew laws and reforms are welcomed, but
OL,15,Fshould have been basic requirements
OL,16,Ffor a developed country such as ours.
OL,18,F"Nevertheless let's move forward in
OL,19,Fthe right direction."
