OL,5,CInquiry
OL,7,FEarlier this month, the Government
OL,8,Fannounced the tower, the remains of
OL,9,Fwhich have stood in place in west
OL,10,FLondon since the fire almost eight
OL,11,Fyears ago, will be "carefully"
OL,12,Fdemolished in a process likely to take
OL,13,Ftwo years.
OL,15,FPolice and prosecutors have previously
OL,16,Fsaid investigators would need until
OL,17,Fthe end of 2025 to complete their
OL,18,Finquiry into the fire, with final
OL,19,Fdecisions on potential criminal
OL,20,Fcharges by the end of 2026.
